## Limitations
- ML was applied as an exploratory exercise — with only 6 samples results are unreliable and should not be used for biological conclusions
- Normal healthy tissues only — no endometriosis patient samples included
- Findings represent a molecular baseline — not direct evidence of disease mechanisms
- Future validation in larger endometriosis patient cohorts is needed



